msgid "Dashboard"
msgstr "Dashboard"

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:40
msgid "An overview of Minimal Map sections and upcoming data tools."
msgstr ""
"Ein Überblick über die Minimal Map-Bereiche und kommende Datenwerkzeuge."

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:43
msgid "Analytics"
msgstr "Statistiken"

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:44
msgid ""
"Review map search demand and identify where people are looking for locations."
msgstr ""
"Überprüfe die Suchanfragen und erkenne, wo Nutzer nach Standorten suchen."

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:47
#: includes/locations/class-location-post-type.php:130
msgid "Locations"
msgstr "Standorte"

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:48
msgid "Create and organize the places you want to render on your maps."
msgstr ""
"Erstelle und organisiere die Orte, die du auf deinen Karten anzeigen "
"möchtest."

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:51
#: includes/collections/class-collection-post-type.php:46
msgid "Collections"
msgstr "Sammlungen"

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:52
msgid ""
"Assemble reusable groups of locations and manage their map-ready assignments."
msgstr ""
"Stelle wiederverwendbare Gruppen von Standorten zusammen und verwalte ihre "
"kartentauglichen Zuweisungen."

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:55
#: includes/tags/class-tag-taxonomy.php:52
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Schlagwörter"

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:56
msgid "Apply lightweight labels to keep map content easy to organize."
msgstr ""
"Verwende leichte Beschriftungen, damit Karteninhalte leicht zu organisieren "
"bleiben."

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:59
#: includes/logos/class-logo-post-type.php:41
msgid "Logos"
msgstr "Logos"

#: includes/admin/class-admin-menu.php:60
